snippet.title: Sadboii Team
snippet.description: Sadboii Team is a team of Asians located in Toronto! We first started as a podcast and we'll be moving into a variety of content soon! For the podcast, we have two hosts, Lucas Po and Russel Lok, and we talk a lot about our lives and experiences growing up in the Asian culture as minorities and doing our best to provide the best advice to life's greatest questions and struggles. We also look at current news and sidetrack into completely random and turbulent topics!
